highlights.text: “Parachute” by Hayley Williams is the highest new entry on Viral Songs USA at #4.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs USA. “Tears” is the highest at #7.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs USA the longest, at 85 days straight.
“The Night The Lights Went Out In Georgia” by Reba McEntire is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs USA, up 16 spots at #67.
